# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .gitignore — Anomaly Detection Project (GitHub + Streamlit Share)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Use Command Prompt (cmd) for the steps in GIT_PUSH_STEPS.md
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ---- Do not push: Proposal folder (avoids "Filename too long" on Windows) ----
Unit Trust Anomaly Detection ML Model - Proposal/
**/Unit Trust Anomaly Detection ML Model - Proposal/

# ---- Do not push: article and presentation ----
article/
presentation/

# ---- Unnecessary .md (keep only main: README.md, deployment/*.md, streamlit_app/README.md, fastapi_app/README.md) ----
/PROJECT_STATUS.md
/MainMarkdown.md
/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md

# ---- Excel and CSV (do not push) ----
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.xlsb
*.csv

# ---- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual environments (do not push)
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env/
ENV/

# Environment and secrets (never push)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.env

# ---- Jupyter ----
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ---- LaTeX build artifacts (keep .tex, ignore generated) ----
*.log
*.aux
*.nav
*.out
*.toc
*.synctex
*.synctex.gz
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk

# ---- Model binaries (large; regenerate with retrain_and_save_keras.py) ----
# Uncomment the two lines below if your repo is too large for GitHub (>100MB file or slow push)
# *.keras
# *.joblib

# ---- IDE and editors ----
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ---- OS ----
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ---- EDA plots (long names hit Windows path limit) ----
eda/eda_plots/
eda/plots/
**/eda_plots/
**/eda/plots/
*clientriskthreshhold*
*clientsubtype*

# ---- Large data (over GitHub 50 MB limit; avoid push warnings) ----
ml/anomalies/
ml/explanations/
# eda/plots/*.png
# ml/plots/**/*.png

# ---- Backups (do not push) ----
*.backup.ipynb
*.bak
*.tmp
*.temp
*.orig

# ---- Logs and temp ----
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/
.cache/
